---
title: Mushroom & Double Bacon Spaghetti Boscaiola with Rocket & Pear Salad
description: This spaghetti dish pairs the earthy flavours of mushrooms with an easy creamy sauce. The side salad balances the richness of the pasta with a sweet and juicy pear.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/672d6156ba086597486322b4-56e9e5c8.jpeg
